  "ui.guide.reset": "Reset Tutorial",
  "ui.guide.body": "[b]Core Loop[/b]\n1. Open Build Prep in the lobby.\n2. Move loot from stash into your current build.\n3. Choose a Beacon or start a Baseline Dive.\n4. Dive, loot, and decide when to extract.\n\n[b]Build Prep[/b]\n- Left side is stash.\n- Right side is your current build.\n- Quick Equip is the fastest way to start a run.\n\n[b]Run Basics[/b]\n- Your character attacks automatically.\n- Movement and extraction timing are your main decisions.\n- Press [Z] to pull nearby loot.\n- Press [I], [K], [M] to open build panels during a run.\n\n[b]Risk And Reward[/b]\n- Extracting secures your current rewards.\n- Failing a run loses backpack loot.\n- Beacons change depth, lives, and run modifiers."
